Welcome to Vero Wine Bar
/$
$
Vero Wine Bar is a place where the love for wine and the joy of gathering intertwine. Our story begins with a passion for curating the finest wines from around the world and creating a welcoming space for wine enthusiasts and novices alike. We take pride in offering a diverse selection of wines, craft beer, sake, tapas, flatbreads, and delectable desserts. Our team is dedicated to providing a unique experience that transcends the ordinary, making Vero Wine Bar a standout destination on Main Street in historic downtown Vero Beach, Florida.

$
Meet the Owners
/$
$
Meet Maria and David, world travelers who believe the best stories are shared over the perfect glass of wine. Their passion for hospitality comes to life in this cozy, elevated spot designed for wine lovers, book clubs, date night, getting together with the girls, and anyone seeking a little charm and escape.
​
From rare imports and small-vineyard selections to savory bites and craft beers perfect after a round of golf — everything here invites you to sit, sip, and stay awhile.
​
Maria's Spanish family roots love tapas and "Sobremesa" was part of Sunday gatherings after church, she loves to share that tradition with simple yet complex flavors in bite size morsels that go perfectly with a wine tasting.
​
David grew up sailing the Narragansett Bay on the weekends on his father's sailboat and loves to hear about your adventures while he pours your new favorite craft brew to go with your pizza.
